attributes.action: Abolish the TV licence and make the BBC a subscription channel
attributes.additional_details: The licence is more expensive than a lot of subscriptions, and I believe we should have the choice as to whether we pay to watch it.
attributes.background: Abolish the TV licence and replace with subscription for those who want to watch it.
